persona_hints: [role-ba]

intent: |
  BA leads a structured discovery before contract signature so the SoW reflects real complexity
  rather than wishful pitch numbers. End state — agency / outsource shop submits a bid backed by
  traced assumptions, evidenced estimates, explicit out-of-scope list, and a risk register the
  sponsor has seen.

